      "content": "thanks. i see what u mean about making the subject do the action. i guess i just find it annoying how passive voice can kind of hide the actual actor in the sentence, making things feel vague or indirect. is there a specific reason why it's considered bad in academic writing?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
